息觀，合稱二甘露門，也是五停心觀之一。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%8D%E6%B7%A8%E8%A7%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B7%25A8%25E8%25A7%2580&d=7M2MF2%2FQfIbUl1XzgL2gNozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b1ba91fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%8D%E6%B7%A8%E8%A7%80</a><br />\n<br />\n不淨觀屬於四念處中的身念處[11]，又可分成觀察自身（身至念），以及觀察死亡過程（墓園九觀）兩者。由墓園九觀，又發展出白骨觀。<br />\n<br />\n據《俱舍論》卷二十二、《大智度論》卷十九等載，修此禪觀以對治貪愛色身及欲界男女欲貪為目的。方法是在禪定中觀想自身與他身污穢不淨：<br />\n<br />\n觀自身不淨：觀身死、屍發脹、變青瘀、膿爛、腐朽、蟲吃、骨鎖等；<br />\n觀他身不淨：觀種子不淨（以過去惑業為因，以父母精血為種）、住處不淨（住母胎）、自相不淨（身具九孔，有唾涕大小便等）、自體不淨（由三十二種不淨物組成身體）、終竟不淨（身死後或土埋成土，或蟲吃成糞，或火燒成灰）。修此禪觀以消除對人生的貪戀，堅定出世修行的決心。<br />\n觀自身<br />\n如同以意念進行人體解剖，修行者以組成自己身體的器官、體液、填充物等為觀想對象。根據經典，區分為《南傳大藏經》的三十一物[12]，漢傳《雜阿含經》[13]及《中阿含經》[11][14]的三十二物，以及《大般若經》[15]及《大毗婆沙論》的三十六物[16]。漢傳佛教所傳，主要為觀三十六物，南傳佛教的傳承則為三十二身份。<br />\n<br />\n觀他身<br />\n在墓園、森林或街道，觀察屍體的腐敗與分解過程。在禪修時，憶想起屍體的影像，以此進行禪修[17]。<br />\n<br />\n觀入胎<br />\n觀想從精卵結合開始，身體的發育過程[18]。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學佛TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkbodhigarden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkbodhigarden&d=7M2MF2%2FQfIbUl1XzgL2gNozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7a662c43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkbodhigarden</a>"},{"pid":"6e28d0798e48b47fc679435b471c92f1802e9f30","tid":900922,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbfe601b269acd89d0c10bf73a0d296a3e8714f1","tid":900922,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"除左切丁有咩辦法?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:01:20.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B3%A2%E5%A3%AB%E9%A0%93%C2%B7%E7%A7%91%E8%B2%9D%E7%89%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E9%25A0%2593%25C2%25B7%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%25B2%259D%25E7%2589%25B9&d=7M2MF2%2FQfIbUl1XzgL2gNozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d90bd9e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B3%A2%E5%A3%AB%E9%A0%93%C2%B7%E7%A7%91%E8%B2%9D%E7%89%B9</a><br />\n<br />\n在1858年7月16日，為了抗拒性交易的誘惑，他用剪刀閹了自己，並丟棄生殖器，然後他在找醫生前吃了一餐並參加了一場禱告。"},{"pid":"e12f121403e3c02fa6e721091e4cb65c450b4bfe","tid":900922,"uid":75745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"戒唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42063d72b4213d0099e34553fdf3168894a1531","tid":900922,"uid":196701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"割咗兩粒春子都可以"},{"pid":"b9a3a38a5ee974b36fe850a282e71514eaf189ae","tid":900922,"uid":190708,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"大家唔洗驚,樓主岩岩打完j入左聖人mode姐,好快無事架啦"},{"pid":"f3157eec50cb70f548b6230aa7d3cc3a0b160fe4","tid":900922,"uid":100550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:25:08.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐仲未見蕭巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aded1b3b17672241be8e64d052725dc78b29981","tid":900922,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0506ff2ba7b1a3ca207f2e639d47a7150ee9c11e","tid":900922,"uid":9450,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"736c7792b68696ba841434aa6c8ba4051f189732","tid":900922,"uid":14269,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:50:34.000Z","msg":"搵份會累到仆街既工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家日日收左工淨係諗訓覺，機都唔想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"打開丁既人做牛工都會照打<br />\n以前中學暑期工返地盤都照打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:26:58.000Z","msg":"老咗自然不丁～"},{"pid":"2261b6c4d76b5c67714424dce5df7ab169da1846","tid":900922,"uid":221463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T17:30:38.000Z","ms